:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大陸食品出名多化學野 個火鍋賣相又唔吸引 成pat屎咁 又多油 啲人食哂成個元素週期表落肚都仲要笑笑口話好撚正 真係好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>死窮鬼冇$食啊?</blockquote>50幾蚊好貴咩<br />\n<br />\n咁都拎到優越感<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屎嚟嘅仲要係中國嘅屎<br />\n咁都要畀 50 蚊去食<br />\n我就真係寧願做窮鬼喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>加多十蚊都可以去大家樂打邊爐 做咩要食啲化學野</blockquote>呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n海底撈邊有50蚊咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0c551751bbc0f4a4388ef9941daa44c14e6ff6","tid":509533,"uid":9348,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"d 死on9有飯唔食食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110949fbe4d78ca9b926d50e00373f30fbfda418","tid":509533,"uid":74531,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"理性討論<br />\n<br />\n先唔講香港邊爐有幾正同麻辣火鍋既比較。<br />\n<br />\n剩講麻辣火鍋本身海底撈個麻辣火鍋已經算係差個堆，服務好就無得拗，你話上去實店到享受下做廢人皇帝都可以理解，特登買個貴到pk既化學自熱火鍋真係唔知做咩鳩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入面d料全部都係唔新鮮廢料+一堆菜，加埋個同正宗四川重慶個種老火鍋差幾十皮，既得個油字又唔香得個種科學辣，辣嘴辣胃既垃圾湯底，直係狗也不屌。仲要分分鐘貴過去食一餐正既麻辣火鍋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n得個班垃圾偽網紅仲要話到好好食，真係on99,真係要食d大陸狗都會叫個d火鍋便當外賣。係得班平時食開屎同有錢咩到得既網紅先會話好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b412b3ed3620e1f19d8dfaa32c6e1bc2f09ed3","tid":509533,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T16:45:13.000Z","msg":"<blo